) cleft (
<number box="[620,658,1811,1837]" pageId="15" pageNumber="16" value="0.7">0.7</number>
X), each lobe blunt at apex, with 
<number box="[1064,1079,1811,1837]" pageId="15" pageNumber="16" value="1.0">1</number>
apical robust seta and 
<number box="[1351,1360,1811,1837]" pageId="15" pageNumber="16" value="1.0">1</number>
apical plumose setae.
</paragraph>
